{"title_page": "T\u00e2n Y\u00ean District", "text_new": "{{Expand Vietnamese|T\u00e2n Y\u00ean|date=March 2009}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = T\u00e2n Y\u00ean District\n|settlement_type        = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = Huy\u1ec7n T\u00e2n Y\u00ean\n|nickname               = \n|motto                  = \n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = \n|pushpin_label_position = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Vietnam}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces of Vietnam|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[B\u1eafc Giang Province|B\u1eafc Giang]]\n|subdivision_type2      = \n|subdivision_name2      = \n|seat_type              = Capital\n|seat                   = [[Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, B\u1eafc Giang|Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng]]\n|government_type        =\n|leader_title           = \n|leader_name            = \n| leader_title1          = Party Secretary:\n| leader_name1           = L\u00e2m Th\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00e0nh<ref>http://www.bacgiang.gov.vn/email/c-214/timkiem.html&c=0</ref>\n| leader_title2          = People's Council Chairman:\n| leader_name2           = D\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00f4 M\u1ea1nh\n| leader_title3          = People's Committee Chairman:  <!-- for places with, say, both a mayor and a city manager -->\n| leader_name3           = L\u00e2m Th\u1ecb H\u01b0\u01a1ng Th\u00e0nh\n|established_title      =  \n|established_date       = \n|area_magnitude         = \n|unit_pref              = Imperial<!--Enter: Imperial, if Imperial (metric) is desired-->\n|area_footnotes         = \n|area_total_km2         = 203.7 \n|area_land_km2          = \n|area_water_km2         = \n|area_total_sq_mi       = \n|area_land_sq_mi        = \n|area_water_sq_mi       = \n|area_water_percent     = \n|area_urban_km2         = \n|area_urban_sq_mi       = \n|area_metro_km2         = \n|area_metro_sq_mi       = \n|population_as_of       =2003\n|population_footnotes   = \n|population_note        = \n|population_total       = 161835 \n|population_density_km2 = \n|population_density_sq_mi = \n|population_metro       =\n|population_density_metro_km2 =\n|population_density_metro_sq_mi =\n|population_urban       = \n|population_density_urban_km2 =\n|population_density_urban_mi2 =\n| timezone = UTC + 7\n| utc_offset = +7\n|latd=|latm=|lats=|latNS=\n|longd=|longm=|longs= |longEW=\n|elevation_footnotes    =  <!--for references: use <ref> </ref> tags-->\n|elevation_m              = \n|elevation_ft           = \n|postal_code_type       =  <!-- enter ZIP code, Postcode, Post code, Postal code... -->\n|postal_code            =\n|area_code              = \n|website                = \n|footnotes              = \n}}\n'''T\u00e2n Y\u00ean''' is a [[huy\u1ec7n|rural district]] of [[B\u1eafc Giang Province]] in the [[Northeast (Vietnam)|Northeast]] region of Vietnam. As of 2003 the district had a population of 161,835.<ref name=\"Statoids\">{{cite web|url=http://www.statoids.com/yvn.html|title=Districts of Vietnam|publisher=Statoids|accessdate=March 13, 2009}}</ref> The district covers an area of 204&nbsp;km\u00b2. The district capital lies at [[Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, B\u1eafc Giang|Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng]].<ref name=\"Statoids\"/>\n\n==Administrative divisions==\nThe district is divided administratively into two townships: [[Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng, B\u1eafc Giang|Cao Th\u01b0\u1ee3ng]] (the capital) and [[Nh\u00e3 Nam]], and into the following communes:\n\n#[[Qu\u1ebf Nham]]\n#[[Vi\u1ec7t L\u1eadp]]\n#[[Li\u00ean Chung]]\n#[[Cao X\u00e1, B\u1eafc Giang|Cao X\u00e1]]\n#[[Ng\u1ecdc L\u00fd]]\n#[[Ng\u1ecdc Thi\u1ec7n]]\n#[[Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u, B\u1eafc Giang|Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u]]\n#[[Ng\u1ecdc V\u00e2n]]\n#[[H\u1ee3p \u0110\u1ee9c, B\u1eafc Giang|H\u1ee3p \u0110\u1ee9c]]\n#[[Ph\u00fac H\u00f2a]]\n#[[T\u00e2n Trung, B\u1eafc Giang|T\u00e2n Trung]]\n#[[An D\u01b0\u01a1ng, B\u1eafc Giang|An D\u01b0\u01a1ng]]\n#[[Lan Gi\u1edbi]]\n#[[Nh\u00e3 Nam]]\n#[[\u0110\u1ea1i H\u00f3a]]\n#[[Quang Ti\u1ebfn, B\u1eafc Giang|Quang Ti\u1ebfn]]\n#[[Ph\u00fac S\u01a1n, T\u00e2n Y\u00ean|Ph\u00fac S\u01a1n]]\n#[[Lam C\u1ed1t]]\n#[[Vi\u1ec7t Ng\u1ecdc]]\n#[[Song V\u00e2n]]\n#[[Li\u00ean S\u01a1n, B\u1eafc Giang|Li\u00ean S\u01a1n]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n{{coord|21.383|N|106.133|E|type:adm2nd_region:VN|display=title}}\n\n{{Districts of Northeast Vietnam}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tan Yen District}}\n[[Category:Districts of B\u1eafc Giang Province]]\n{{BacGiang-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Expand Vietnamese|T\u00e2n Y\u00ean|date=March 2009}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n|name                   = T\u00e2n Y\u00ean District\n|settlement_type        = [[Huy\u1ec7n|District]]\n|official_name          = \n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = Huy\u1ec7n T\u00e2n Y\u00ean\n|nickname               = \n|motto                  = \n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_blank_emblem     =\n|blank_emblem_size      =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           =\n|pushpin_map            = \n|pushpin_label_position = \n|subdivision_type       = Country\n|subdivision_name       = {{flag|Vietnam}}\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Provinces 